%^BOLD%^-=%^RESET%^%^MAGENTA%^Nightmare Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

You live in the deepest darkest nightmares of your foes, and their screams fuel your dark power.

Clerics with the Nightmare Domain gain the following features:
- +1 Spell DC when casting illusion school spells
- %^MAGENTA%^Nightmare%^RESET%^ as an innate spell.

The nightmare domain contains the following spells:

Doom, Black Tentacles, Shadow Enchantment, False Vision, Weird

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Ashra

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^